{"tid":1640280,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"《國際戰線》Twitter戰友，小弟有野想請教","createTime":"2019-10-09T01:55:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T12:50:39.000Z","uid":298324,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5350c0ae404152626e3aa4034d7e7d6d3e3c053a","tid":1640280,"uid":298324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T01:55:12.000Z","msg":"究竟點樣可以避免/減低Twitter懷疑你係bot<br />\n既機會? <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係好清楚咩玩法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46d7467b0804c50bf398c7530e35258185d4f5cf","tid":1640280,"uid":38864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:16:57.000Z","msg":"同問<br />\n今朝瘋狂rt (有comment)，有reply tweet，晏少少再開就話有unusual activity lock咗個account<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae3150c00b66ca67f4a5d12021ecafb686c20cee","tid":1640280,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:23:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">全球「和尼畫」<br />\n#XinniethePooh Challenge</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1640322/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1640322/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rG1sQ5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrG1sQ5b.jpg&h=d6b3d577&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K9NvORS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK9NvORS.jpg&h=fcaaa2a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「和尼畫」挑戰<br />\n1.畫出你心中所想的維尼圖<br />\n2.留下你想對習維尼講嘅說話<br />\n3.放上ig、fb、twitter，tag #XinniethePooh<br />\n4.tag 1-3個你想佢一齊畫維尼嘅朋友<br />\n5.被tag嘅朋友一齊畫維尼，讓愛與維尼佔領地球，推到畀習維尼本人見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「Xinnie the Pooh」Challenge<br />\n1. Draw your own &quot;Xinnie the Pooh&quot;<br />\n2. Write down what do you want to tell Chairman Xi<br />\n3. Post your work on instagram, facebook and twitter with tag #Xinnie the Pooh<br />\n4. Tag up to 3 more friends to ask them draw together!<br />\n5. Those who are tagged also join to draw Xinnie the Pooh, keep drawing until Chairman Xi can see our works!!"},{"pid":"76a2c836a4072a685c9630ca3c74074b4f8c4d5d","tid":1640280,"uid":56978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:50:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}